d.ja: 第一者による行動の規約は、賭けの結果次第である; 大部分の司法管区では法令により施行できない

d.en: a contract for maintenance services
d.ja: 保守サービスの契約

d.en: a contract in which you agree to purchase all your requirements of a particular sort from one party
d.ja: ある団体から特定のものにおいて、要求を全て適えるために、同意した契約

d.en: contract between employer and employee
d.da: kontrakt mellem en arbejdsgiver og en arbejdstager…
d.de: Vertrag zwischen Arbeitgeber und Arbeitnehmer
d.ro: contract încheiat de un salariat cu o întreprindere sau cu o instituție, prin care cel dintâi se obligă să presteze în favoarea celei din urmă o anumită muncă în schimbul unui salariu
d.ja: 雇用者と従業員の間の契約

d.en: an implicit agreement among people that results in the organization of society; individual surrenders liberty in return for protection
d.ro: Acord implicit între persoane, care rezultă în organizarea societății
d.ja: 社会を組織化するにいたった人の間の暗黙の合意; 個人が保護を得る代わりに自由を放棄すること

d.en: a one-sided agreement whereby you promise to do (or refrain from doing) something in return for a performance (not a promise)
d.ja: （約束ではない）ある履行の返礼に何かをする（またはしない）ことを約束する一方的な合意

d.en: an agreement that is not in writing and is not signed by the parties but is a real existing contract that lacks only the formal requirement of a memorandum to render it enforceable in litigation
d.ja: 書かれておらず、当事者によって署名されていないが、訴訟において強制できるようにする覚え書きの公式の要求を欠くだけの事実上の実在する契約である合意

d.en: the capability or quality of shrinking or contracting, especially by muscle fibers and even some other forms of living matter
d.ro: însușire a țesuturilor organice de a se contracta
d.ja: 特に、筋繊維や、さらには生物のその他の形態によって、縮む、または緊縮する能力あるいは性質
